headline: Nvidia Has 65% of Its Portfolio Invested in 1 Brilliant Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stock
summary: Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) first disclosed a stake in fellow semiconductor company Arm Holdings (NASDAQ: ARM) in the fourth quarter of 2023.  The position was valued at $147 million at the time, but a recently filed Form 13F shows the position is now worth more than $280 million and accounts for about 65% of Nvidia's $433 million stock portfolio.  To be clear, Nvidia has not added to its stake this year.
